    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000003876",
      "line": 4,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "If this unit contains 10 models, one Legionary’s boltgun can be replaced with one of the following:\n• 1 heavy bolter\n• 1 missile launcher"
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000003876",
      "line": 5,
      "button": "•",
      "description": "One Legionary’s boltgun can be replaced with one of the following:\n• 1 flamer\n• 1 meltagun\n• 1 plasma gun"
    },
    {
      "datasheetId": "000003876",
      "line": 6,
